  <!-- EN: Foxhound GPMG -->
  <USAC_HeavyMachineGunMounted.label>猎狐犬机枪</USAC_HeavyMachineGunMounted.label>
  <!-- EN: A multi-purpose heavy machine gun with a lightweight composite material frame and improved design, it is widely used in various weapon platforms and fixed defensive facilities. In the distant past, before materials were almost discontinued due to war, it was a very successful alternative to the M2 heavy machine gun. -->
  <USAC_HeavyMachineGunMounted.description>一种使用复合材料轻量化枪身并改良的多用途重机枪，被广泛使用於各类武器平台与固定防御设施当中，於遥远的地球时代在材料一度因战争短缺而几乎停产前其曾是非常成功的M2重机枪替代品。</USAC_HeavyMachineGunMounted.description>
